name: MovieYearQuiz
0:
”Alexa, begin movie year quiz”
”Alexa, open movie year quiz and start a quiz”
”Alexa, start movie year quiz and quiz me”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: movie year quiz
des: In this skill, user can take a quiz about the year in which a movie was released, or ask for the release year of a movie. Alexa can take a quiz by asking 10 questions about the release year of a movie and the result is summarised at the end of the quiz.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
